name: MultipleGestation
title: Multiple Gestation
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of  values contains diagnoses that represent the delivery twins and higher order multiples .),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who delivered twins or higher order of multiples.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the "Diagnosis" category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD 9 CM codes that identify a delivery of twins or higher order multiples.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
